Text: Grrroarrr!!!
Graaah!
G-Grrgh...
Gotcha!
(I almost forgot how fun it is to hunt!)
And it's all mine... *drool*

(I didn't eat any supper last night, so my stomach is
completely empty.)

(Back at the Shadow Garden they always tell me
no second helpings, but...)
Today it’s all mine! Time to dig in!
Ahhh...!

Oof, I'm stuffed. I don't think I could eat another
bite.

It's starting to get kinda dark, I'd better find
somewhere to curl up for the night...
Uh-oh, looks like rain.
Eep! I'm gonna get soaked!
...There!
Phew, I made it...

Looks like it gets wider further in. 
What if it's a bear's den?
*sniff, sniff*

Hmm... I can't smell anything when the weather
is like this.
Well, it doesn't matter!

(Even if a bear does live here, I'll just take it out
and make a meal of it.)
Guess I ended up stuck indoors here too...

It's just like when I'd been forbidden from going
outside back at base...
But it feels completely different! This is way better!

Not having Lady Alpha here always barking at me is
the best!

(It's true, Lady Alpha is always on my case. I have to
obey her though, because she's strong... Ha-ruff.)

Awooo! I can't get hung up on sad stuff now that I'm
finally having fun!
...Is someone there?
What?!
...Nope, no one's here!
Then who's talking?!

(I can make out a scent as whoever it is comes closer.
The scent of a therianthrope...and blood.)
Are you...injured?
Oh, you're one of us...
Wait, is this your territory?

(Each tribe of therianthrope has its own territory...
So it's possible that this cave belongs to this one.)

(I could give her a beating and take it for myself by
force...but only a weakling picks on someone who's
in a bad state!)

Sorry, I completely missed it. I didn't know this is
your territory. I'll move on, so—
Why leave? In our world only the strong survive.

You should be able to thrash me and take this place
for yourself no problem.
Ha-ruff...
(...She's right. But then why do I feel this way?)
(Even I don't really understand...)
...I'm full right now!
...Heh.
Hahaha, you're a funny one. Never met anyone like you.

Hey, lemme ask you somethin'. I haven't seen you
around these parts before—

So are you part of a pack somewhere? Don't see getup
like yours every day.

(Pack... Hearing that makes me remember the faces of
Boss, Alpha, and the others—)

(But, I try to clear all that outta my head. I puff my
chest out proudly and give her my answer!)
...I'm strong, so I'm fine on my own!
